// material
import { Box, Grid, Container, Typography, Stack, item } from '@mui/material';
// components
import Page from '../components/Page';
import {
  AppTasks,
  AppNewUsers,
  AppBugReports,
  AppItemOrders,
  AppNewsUpdate,
  AppWeeklySales,
  AppOrderTimeline,
  AppCurrentVisits,
  AppWebsiteVisits,
  AppTrafficBySite,
  AppCurrentSubject,
  AppConversionRates,
  AppWarningsReports
} from '../components/_dashboard/app';

// ----------------------------------------------------------------------

export default function DashboardApp() {
  return (
    <Page title="Dashboard">
      <Container maxWidth="xl">
        <Box sx={{ pb: 5 }}>
          <Typography style={{ color: '#45a29e' }} variant="h4">
            Hi FÃ©lix, Here's what happening!
          </Typography>
        </Box>

        <Grid container spacing={{ xs: 1, sm: 2, lg: 3 }} columns={{ xs: 8, sm: 8, md: 8, lg: 8 }}>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Stack spacing={2}>
              <item>
                <AppBugReports />
              </item>
              <item>
                <AppWarningsReports />
              </item>
            </Stack>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={5}>
            <AppOrderTimeline />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={9}>
            <AppWebsiteVisits />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={4}>
            <AppCurrentVisits />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={4}>
            <AppCurrentSubject />
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Page>
  );
}
